We manufacture flame retardant chemicals for : acrylonitrile-butadiene-styrene (ABS), acrylic ester-styrene-acrylonitrile (ASA), AES (acrylonitrile-ethylene propylene-styrene), Styrene-acrylonitrile copolymers (SAN), polymethyl methacrylate (PMMA), styrene-methyl methacrylate (SMMA), polycarbonate (PC), polyamide (PA) or polybutylene terephthalate (PBT) for a wide range of applications.



The company has been concentrating on developing new environment-friendly Flame

Retardants and Smoke Suppressants in close cooperation with various major industries and

research institutes. We have been bringing in new technology and new material in process of

product development, and therefore have established a strong and stable R&D process.


Our technical innovation and high product Quality receives recognition and trust of the

customers, which leads the company to a continuous growth in the market of Flame Retardant Chemicals and creation of its own brand name NIKNAM.


Being in this industry for the last three decades our products are readily & regularly accepted

& Consumed by various major manufacturing industries across India & the World. Possessing a group of experts of international prestige and long industrial experience, we have established a wide range of markets for our products. With Automatic production lines our annual installed production capacity is more than 60,000 Metric Tons of Flame Retardant Chemicals & fillers.





