Omya Performance Polymer Distribution AG
OPPD is a global leader with more than 60 years of experience, innovation and expertise in the distribution and application development of thermoplastic polymers and elastomers.

Our team of highly experienced sales people are able to meet your requirements and exceed your expectations whilst adding value to your business.

The team is supported in all markets by our development engineers who have unrivalled knowledge of all aspects of polymer technology, including part and mould design, selection of polymers to achieve the best performance, troubleshooting and optimization of part production.

Our long-term partnerships with world-class suppliers strengthen our knowledge and provide us with an extensive range of high-quality products to offer a material solution for every application. All our suppliers are REACH compliant and all OPPD companies are fully ISO 9001:2015 certified.

The OPPD portfolio includes products and solutions that meet the requirements of leading and emerging industries.

The range is accompanied by certifications and approvals for the automotive, medical, food and electrical industries. Strategically located warehouses help us to offer customized supply solutions worldwide. Materials are available from 25 kg bags to full truckloads, octabins, big bags and bulk deliveries. If required, we can repackage the material into the required packaging at our warehouse.
