SIMONA AG
Thermoplastic solutions tailored to end-user needs – SIMONA at K

The company with the strongest focus on end users of thermoplastic solutions. This is the long-term objective that SIMONA has set itself. In pursuit of this goal, the company has evolved its former product-driven organisational structure into an application-oriented one. Five business lines form the core of this structure: Industry, Infrastructure, Advertising & Building, Mobility and Aquaculture. Underpinned by strong regional sales activities, acknowledged product management and a well-established technical service centre, the newly created business lines will serve the market segments of these applications in close cooperation with trading partners in the engineering plastics sector.  This year''s K in Düsseldorf will provide SIMONA with a suitable platform to showcase its extensive range of products and services in the application areas covered by the business lines. Adopting the motto "Part of Life. Part of the Solution.“, the company will also be unveiling a host of new products.
