Symplast Kimya San. ve Tic. A.S.
Symplast is a globally operating compounder of thermoplastic elastomers (TPE) and thermoplastic vulcanizates (TPV), founded in 2013 in Izmir—where our headquarters and production facilities are still located today. Our European operations are managed from our branch in Essen, Germany.

We specialize in the development and production of EPDM/PP-based TPV compounds, SEBS- and SBS-based technical TPE compounds, and EPR/PP-based TPO compounds—with a strong focus on the construction, automotive, appliance, and tool industries, as well as the electronics, medical and care sectors, and the consumer goods market. We also offer solutions for impact modification applications.

Close collaboration with our customers, our state-of-the-art R&D laboratory, and our meticulous processes enable us to develop cost-efficient, high-performance TPE compounds with consistently high quality—precisely tailored to our clients’ specific needs and requirements.

Thanks to the location of our production site at an international seaport and our broad network of global distribution partners, we ensure fast and reliable worldwide delivery.
