ility but also provides a clear competitive edge in international markets.“Our IKMIB certification reflects the trust and recognition we have earned from customers and partners around the world,” says Hakan Dügeroglu of Symplast. “At the same time, it supports our vision of becoming a preferred TPE compounder in Europe and beyond.”Symplast continues to invest strategically in production, innovation, and compliance with relevant standards to deliver reliable, high-quality TPE solutions to customers worldwide. | Exhibitors & Products', hall = '5', stand = 'F42', contact_persons = '[{"name": "Anil Ugurlu", "role": "General Manager/Geschäftsführer Symplast GmbH", "email": "", "phone": "", "additional_info": ""}, {"name": "", "role": "", "email": "", "phone": "", "additional_info": ""}, {"name": "", "role": "", "email": "", "phone": "", "additional_info": ""}, {"name": "", "role": "", "email": "", "phone": "", "additional_info": ""}]'::jsonb, scraping_timestamp = '2025-09-18T03:11:12.487553', success = true, scraping_status = 'completed', data_source = 'ultimate_scraping'
